race.description: Bet Nation Same Race Multi 5th Grade
race.comment: FORNER'S REIGN (2) is progressing well and looks close to another win after hitting the frame from Box 7 last run (22.00) at this track. Hard to beat again. LENARD CLYDE (3) placed last time (22.13) at this track in a Grade 5, finishing second and beaten 3 lengths. Can feature with the right run. FREDDY DODGE (1) deserves plenty of thought over this journey. Something for the Multiples: PANAMA LOCO (7)
